    "inputs" : {
    
    
    "items" : [
    
    
    
    "The service life and the appearance of the convertible top are largely dependent on proper care and operation."
    ,
    
    
    "The vehicle should be parked in the shade whenever possible as the fabric, rubber material and colour can be harmed by extended exposure to sunlight."
    ,
    
    
    "In the event of leaks in the convertible top covering or seams or in the folded sections, use the Porsche convertible top care product."
    ,
    
    
    "Do not use the Porsche convertible top care product on painted surfaces, glass or on the rear window; if this is used, remove the product immediately."
    ,
    
    
    "Do not remove stains on the convertible top with petrol, stain remover, benzene, paint thinner or other solvents; they attack the rubber layer between the fabrics and diminish the water-tightness and service life of the convertible top."
    ,
    
    
    "Recommendation: Treat the convertible top covering with the Porsche convertible top care product twice a year or before installing the hardtop (winter driving)."
    
    ]
    
    }
    
    }
    ,
    
    {
    
    
